# Brand & Frontend Redesign Scope

## Brand positioning

GujjuTicks is a **software startup** that provides **custom apps**, **websites**, and **custom software** for startups and growing businesses — not a Gujarati community portal.

When writing copy, meta, or UI for redesign pages:

- Lead with custom apps, websites, and software delivery — clear B2B / startup language.
- Prefer practical service outcomes (MVP, launch, operations tools) over culture or community framing.
- Do **not** link to Cities, AI Prompts, or Post Builder from Home, nav, Contact, Blogs, or other marketing surfaces. Those modules stay live at their URLs but are unlisted from public entry points.

## Redesign (new design)

Apply the new frontend design to:

- Home
- Blogs
- Contact
- Services (`/services`, `/services/{slug}`)
- Technology (`/technology`, `/technology/{slug}`)
- Work (`/work`, `/work/{slug}`)
- About
- CMS detail pages (`/p/{slug}` from dashboard Pages)
- Cities list (`/cities`), city detail (`/city/{slug}`), category listings (`/city/{slug}/{category}`), business directory hub (`/business`), and add business (`/business/add`) — use `page="cities"` and [`public/css/site/cities.css`](public/css/site/cities.css)
- AI Prompts list (`/ai-prompts`), category (`/ai-prompts/{slug}`), and detail (`/ai-prompt/{slug}`) — light animated design matching Home (`page="ai-prompts"`, [`public/css/site/ai-prompts.css`](public/css/site/ai-prompts.css), [`public/js/site/ai-prompts.js`](public/js/site/ai-prompts.js))
- Post Builder list (`/news-post`) and detail / generator (`/news-post/{slug}`) — light animated news/letters design (`page="news-post"`, [`public/css/site/news-post.css`](public/css/site/news-post.css), [`public/js/site/news-post.js`](public/js/site/news-post.js))
- Image creator / editor (`/image-editor/{slug}`) — light studio design (`page="image-editor"`, [`public/css/site/image-editor.css`](public/css/site/image-editor.css), [`public/js/site/image-editor.js`](public/js/site/image-editor.js))
- News hub (`/news`) and category detail (`/news/{slug}`) — light animated news desk design (`page="news"`, [`public/css/site/news.css`](public/css/site/news.css), [`public/js/site/news.js`](public/js/site/news.js))

Shared marketing pages use `page="marketing"` and [`public/css/site/marketing.css`](public/css/site/marketing.css).

## Remove

Remove these pages from the site (routes, nav links, and related UI entry points):

- Resume Builder
- Free Online Courses
- Capabilities *(redirected to Services)*

## Unlisted modules

Cities, AI Prompts, Post Builder, Image Editor, and News remain available by direct URL. Do not add or restore links to them from Home, shared nav, Contact, Blogs, or other marketing surfaces.
